{
  "chapter_id": "lecture-01-association-1",
  "course_id": "user-1-comp7103",
  "lesson_id": "u1-comp7103-association-1",
  "mode": "guided_story",
  "screens": [
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "support",
        "confidence"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "一条规则好不好，需要两个指标来衡量。",
        "一个是<term id=\"support\">支持度</term>，一个是<term id=\"confidence\">置信度</term>。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "支持度 = sup(X ∪ Y) / 总交易数 N。",
        "它告诉我们这条规则覆盖了多少交易。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "支持度太低，说明规则只适用于极少数情况，没什么用。",
        "所以我们会设一个最低支持度阈值 ρₛ。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "置信度 = sup(X ∪ Y) / sup(X)。",
        "它衡量的是：买了 X 的人里，有多少也买了 Y。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "置信度越高，规则越可靠。",
        "我们也会设一个最低置信度阈值 ρ_c。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "来看一个例子。",
        "数据集有 25 笔交易，ρₛ = 20%，ρ_c = 65%。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "考虑规则 {f} ⇒ {a, b}。",
        "sup({a, b, f}) = 2，sup({f}) = 3。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "支持度 = 2/25 = 8%，小于 20%。",
        "置信度 = 2/3 ≈ 67%，大于 65%。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "这条规则置信度达标，但支持度太低。",
        "它只在少数交易中成立，不够普遍，所以不会被采纳。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "exercise": {
        "answers": [
          "0.4",
          "40%"
        ],
        "explanation": "支持度 = 4 / 10 = 0.4，即 40%。",
        "kind": "fill_in_blank",
        "prompt": "支持度 = ?"
      },
      "id": "s020",
      "lines": [
        "如果 sup({面包, 牛奶}) = 4，总交易数 N = 10。",
        "规则 {面包} ⇒ {牛奶} 的支持度是多少？"
      ],
      "type": "exercise"
    }
  ],
